data.description:
Photos coming on Friday 9th.  
Very nice and well cared for 3-2-2 brick home is located near DFW Airport and is walking distance from Towne Lake Park which offers a beautiful lake and walking trails. The low maintenance backyard is private and perfect for pets!  This home is move in ready. Roof was replaced in 2019 and added radiant barrier insulation. HVAC is new (2020) with added ductwork.  This great neighborhood is well maintained and convenient to DFW freeways.
Security camera system to be removed by owner.
